extend _component/layout/base

block config
    -
        var title= "Welcome to Quick Blog"
        var description= "Use suuuper QuickBlog as it is easy and get 100/100 score from Google pagespeed insights"
block content
    .welcome
        h1=title
        p.welcome__description=description
        a.scroll-down(href="#continue")
            span Click to continue reading or scroll down   
            span.continue-arrow
    .content
        #continue
        p.lead Don’t let the things you are afraid of—failure, change, adversity, the unknown—stop you from going after the things you want most. Instead, find the courage to do what scares you. Face your fears, and you’ll uncover new and great opportunities. And it will feel good.
        p 
            small “Avoiding danger is no safer in the long run than outright exposure. The fearful are caught as often as the bold.” —Helen Keller
        p
            small “One of the greatest discoveries a man makes, one of his great surprises, is to find he can do what he was afraid he couldn’t do.” —Henry Ford